description: This is a market on if the DeFi Dominance metric, according to CoinGecko, will be 5.15% or higher on April 25, 2021, 12:30 PM ET. This market will resolve to “Yes“ if DeFi Dominance is listed as being 5.15% or higher on the resolution date, and "No" otherwise. The resolution source for this market will be the metric currently listed on https://www.coingecko.com/en/defi as “DeFi Dominance". The non-rounded data as shown on the 'Dominance' chart will be prioritized for the resolution of this market. Specifically, the most recent datapoint listed on the hourly chart as of 12:30 ET on April 25, 2021 will be referenced. The correct dominance percentage can be calculated by subtracting the listed number from one. In the event of ambiguity in terms of the market outcome, the market will be resolved at the sole discretion of the Markets Integrity Committee (MIC).
